{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877638539,"sessionID":"ses_28573097fffenOKKsxrsqAW5XT","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8d73dd001sCmhfjx1BVTrn9","messageID":"msg_d7a8d5c53001z5BOA4EXg23pY4","sessionID":"ses_28573097fffenOKKsxrsqAW5XT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_feb9c6e4f66f4cefbe4278c7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for generating the Kubernetes client-go library for the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-035\n- **Module**: client-go\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: L\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Clientset Generation\n\n### AR-035-001: Clientset Interface\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned`\n- **WHEN** running code-generator with output package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n- **THEN** there SHALL be an `Interface` with `Discovery()` and `RuntimeV1alpha1()` methods\n\n### AR-035-002: Clientset struct\n\n- **GIVEN** the clientset implementation\n- **WHEN** defining the Clientset struct\n- **THEN** it SHALL embed `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`\n\n### AR-035-003: Clientset constructors\n\n- **GIVEN** the Clientset struct\n- **WHEN** creating constructors\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n- **AND** SHALL be `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n- **AND** SHALL be `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\n- **AND** SHALL be `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Typed Client Generation\n\n### AR-035-004: RuntimeV1alpha1Client Interface\n\n- **GIVEN** the typed client package at `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** generating the typed client\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with `RESTClient() rest.Interface` and `AgentRuntimesGetter` / `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n\n### AR-035-005: RuntimeV1alpha1Client struct\n\n- **GIVEN** RuntimeV1alpha1Client implementation\n- **WHEN** defining the client struct\n- **THEN** it SHALL implement `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n- **AND** SHALL have REST defaults: `GroupVersion` = `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.SchemeGroupVersion, `APIPath` = `/apis`\n\n### AR-035-006: AgentRuntime typed client\n\n- **GIVEN** the AgentRuntime typed client\n- **WHEN** defining AgentRuntimeInterface\n- **THEN** it SHALL include Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, DeleteCollection, Get, List, Watch, Patch methods\n- **AND** SHALL embed `AgentRuntimeExpansion`\n\n### AR-035-007: AgentRuntime REST resource\n\n- **GIVEN** AgentRuntimeInterface\n- **WHEN** defining REST resource\n- **THEN** the resource plural SHALL be `agentruntimes`\n- **AND** `AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface` accessor SHALL be defined\n\n### AR-035-008: CodeInterpreter typed client\n\n- **GIVEN** the CodeInterpreter typed client\n- **WHEN** defining CodeInterpreterInterface\n- **THEN** it SHALL have the same method shape as AgentRuntimeInterface\n- **AND** types SHALL be `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`\n- **AND** resource plural SHALL be `codeinterpreters`\n\n### AR-035-009: Expansion hooks\n\n- **GIVEN** the generated expansion file\n- **WHEN** defining expansion interfaces\n- **THEN** there SHALL be empty `AgentRuntimeExpansion` interface\n- **AND** SHALL be empty `CodeInterpreterExpansion` interface\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Scheme Registration\n\n### AR-035-010: Scheme builder\n\n- **GIVEN** the clientset versioned scheme package\n- **WHEN** creating register.go\n- **THEN** there SHALL be a `Scheme` builder function\n- **AND** SHALL be `Codecs` and `ParameterCodec` builders\n- **AND** SHALL provide `AddToScheme` to register runtime/v1alpha1 types\n\n### AR-035-011: Package documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** the scheme package\n- **WHEN** creating doc.go\n- **THEN** it SHALL include package-level documentation\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Informer Factory Generation\n\n### AR-035-012: SharedInformerFactory interface\n\n- **GIVEN** the informers package at `informers/externalversions`\n- **WHEN** generating informers\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `SharedInformerFactory` with Start, Shutdown, WaitForCacheSync, ForResource, InformerFor methods\n- **AND** SHALL have `Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface`\n\n### AR-035-013: SharedInformerFactory constructors\n\n- **GIVEN** SharedInformerFactory\n- **WHEN** creating constructors\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `NewSharedInformerFactory(client versioned.Interface, defaultResync time.Duration)`\n- **AND** SHALL be `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options ...SharedInformerOption)`\n- **AND** Options SHALL include `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n\n### AR-035-014: Runtime group interface\n\n- **GIVEN** the runtime group informer package\n- **WHEN** defining the group interface\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `Interface` with `V1alpha1() v1alpha1.Interface`\n\n### AR-035-015: V1alpha1 version interface\n\n- **GIVEN** the runtime/v1alpha1 informer package\n- **WHEN** defining the version interface\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `Interface` with `AgentRuntimes() AgentRuntimeInformer` and `CodeInterpreters() CodeInterpreterInformer`\n\n### AR-035-016: AgentRuntime informer\n\n- **GIVEN** the AgentRuntime informer\n- **WHEN** defining AgentRuntimeInformer\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n- **AND** SHALL have `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister`\n- **AND** SHALL provide `NewAgentRuntimeInformer`, `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer` constructors\n\n### AR-035-017: CodeInterpreter informer\n\n- **GIVEN** the CodeInterpreter informer\n- **WHEN** defining CodeInterpreterInformer\n- **THEN** it SHALL have the same shape as AgentRuntimeInformer\n- **AND** SHALL provide analogous constructors\n\n### AR-035-018: Generic resource routing\n\n- **GIVEN** the generic informer\n- **WHEN** defining ForResource\n- **THEN** it SHALL route `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\")` to AgentRuntime informer\n- **AND** SHALL route `...WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\")` to CodeInterpreter informer\n\n### AR-035-019: Internal interfaces\n\n- **GIVEN** internalinterfaces package\n- **WHEN** defining interfaces\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `NewInformerFunc` type\n- **AND** SHALL be `SharedInformerFactory` interface with Start and InformerFor\n- **AND** SHALL be `TweakListOptionsFunc` type\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Lister Generation\n\n### AR-035-020: AgentRuntimeLister\n\n- **GIVEN** the listers package at `listers/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** generating AgentRuntimeLister\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `AgentRuntimeLister` with List, AgentRuntimes methods\n- **AND** SHALL embed `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`\n\n### AR-035-021: AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n\n- **GIVEN** AgentRuntimeLister\n- **WHEN** defining namespace lister\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` with List and Get methods\n- **AND** SHALL embed `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`\n- **AND** SHALL use `runtimev1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntime\").GroupResource()`\n\n### AR-035-022: CodeInterpreterLister\n\n- **GIVEN** the listers package\n- **WHEN** generating CodeInterpreterLister\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `CodeInterpreterLister` with same pattern as AgentRuntimeLister\n- **AND** SHALL provide `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister`\n- **AND** SHALL use `Resource(\"codeinterpreter\").GroupResource()`\n\n### AR-035-023: Lister expansion\n\n- **GIVEN** the expansion file\n- **WHEN** defining expansion interfaces\n- **THEN** there SHALL be empty expansion interfaces for all four lister types\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Fake Client Generation\n\n### AR-035-024: Fake clientset\n\n- **GIVEN** the fake clientset package\n- **WHEN** generating fake implementations\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `NewSimpleClientset` and `NewClientset` functions\n- **AND** SHALL be in-memory fake Clientset implementation\n\n### AR-035-025: Fake typed clients\n\n- **GIVEN** the fake typed client package\n- **WHEN** generating fake implementations\n- **THEN** there SHALL be `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` implementing RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n- **AND** SHALL be `FakeAgentRuntimes` implementing AgentRuntimeInterface\n- **AND** SHALL be `FakeCodeInterpreters` implementing CodeInterpreterInterface\n\n### AR-035-026: Fake scheme registration\n\n- **GIVEN** the fake scheme package\n- **WHEN** creating register.go\n- **THEN** it SHALL handle scheme registration for fakes\n- **AND** SHALL provide fake doc.go\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Build Verification\n\n### AR-035-027: Go build succeeds\n\n- **GIVEN** complete client-go generated code\n- **WHEN** running `go build ./client-go/...`\n- **THEN** compilation SHALL succeed without errors\n\n### AR-035-028: Code generation verification\n\n- **GIVEN** the codebase with API types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n- **THEN** client-go SHALL be regenerated correctly\n- **AND** SHALL match the expected structure in deployment/client-go.md\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n- Code generator: k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1\n- Make target: `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775877638498,"end":1775877638535}}}}
